                    "question": "设 $X, Y$ 的概率密度为\n$$\nf(x, y)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}\n1,|y| \\leq x, 0 \\leq x \\leq 1 \\\\\n0, \\quad \\text { 其它 }\n\\end{array}\\right.\n$$\n\n则不正确的是 ( ).",
                    "analysis": "(1) 先求关于 $X$ 与 $Y$ 的边缘密度\n$$\nf_X(x)=\\int_{-x}^x 1 dy = 2x, \\quad 0 \\leq x \\leq 1\n$$\n$$\nf_Y(y)=\\int_{|y|}^1 1 dx = 1-|y|, \\quad -1 \\leq y \\leq 1\n$$\n(2) 计算数字特征\n$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n& E(X)=\\int_0^1 x \\cdot 2 x dx=\\frac{2}{3}, \\quad E\\left(X^2\\right)=\\int_0^1 x^2 \\cdot 2 x dx=\\frac{1}{2} \\\\\n& D(X)=\\frac{1}{2}-\\left(\\frac{2}{3}\\right)^2=\\frac{1}{18} \\\\\n& E(Y)=0, \\quad E\\left(Y^2\\right)=\\int_{-1}^1 y^2(1-|y|) dy=2 \\int_0^1 y^2(1-y) dy=\\frac{1}{6} \\\\\n& D(Y)=\\frac{1}{6}-0=\\frac{1}{6} \\\\\n& E(XY)=\\iint x y f(x,y) dx dy=\\int_0^1 x dx \\int_{-x}^x y dy=0\n\\end{aligned}\n$$\n故 $\\operatorname{cov}(X, Y)=E(XY)-E(X)E(Y)=0$.\n综上所述，选项 $E(XY)=1$ 不正确。",
